column1: # Some data sources report water surface elevation rather than storage volume.
# This file contains the lookup tables to convert elevation (ft) to storage (af).
# - Each location_id can have multiple rows defining the curve
# - Elevations should be in ascending order
# - Linear interpolation is used between points
# - 11507001 (Upper Klamath Lake): 2017 revision of UKL elevation-capacity curve
#   Table includes present configuration with northern marshes and Tulana Farms/Goose Bay
